<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.6.1">
<l>tūviriya malaruḻakkit tuṇaiyōṭum piriyātē</l>
<l>pūviriya matunukarum poṟivariya ciṟuvaṇṭē</l>
<l>tīviriya maṟaivaḷarkkum pukaḻāḷar tiruvāli</l>
<l>ēvariveñ cilaiyāṉuk keṉṉilaimai yuraiyāyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Spotted [and] striped little bee which sucks nectar when the flowers expand,</l>
<l>Without leaving with your love, trampling the blossoms</l>
<l rend="indent">as [your] wings expand,</l>
<l>Tell of my plight to him with the cruel, arrow-nocked bow in sacred Āli</l>
<l>With those of fame who foster the Vedas so that [ritual] flames expand.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
